          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/796.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan (no need to wash it!) to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pak choi</strong> <strong>white bases </strong>(keep the shredded green tops for later) and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 2-3 min, then add the <strong>shredded green tops</strong>, cover and cook for 1-2 min further or until wilted</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/796.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/796.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/796.-step-6-x700.jpg",
