            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>rice</strong> into bowls and add the <strong>crispy pork</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled carrot salad</strong> and <strong>pak choi</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>sesame</strong> <strong>fried egg</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
